snippet.title: The Ba***ds Of Bollywood: Badli Si Hawa Hai (Song) | Aryan | Anirudh, Arijit, Amira| Lakshya, Sahher
snippet.description:
Turn up the volume because it‚Äôs time to groove on the beats of #BadliSiHawaHai! 

Straight from the crazy world of The Ba***ds of Bollywood , the series features Bobby Deol, Lakshya, Sahher Bambba, Manoj Pahwa, Mona Singh, Manish Chaudhari, Raghav Juyal, Anya Singh, Vijayant Kohli, Gautami Kapoor and Rajat Bedi. Written and directed by Aryan Khan and produced by Gauri Khan, this Netflix series is presented by Red Chillies Entertainment. 

Mark your calendars ‚Äì The Ba***ds of Bollywood drops on 18th September only on Netflix, bringing you music, madness, and mayhem!

#TheBadsOfBollywood #BadliSiHawaHai

Composed by Anirudh Ravichander

About YRF Spy Universe:
YRF Spy Universe is a first of its kind cinematic universe of spy thriller films in India. The first film in the universe, "Ek Tha Tiger," starring Salman Khan and Katrina Kaif was released in 2012, followed by its sequel "Tiger Zinda Hai" in 2017. The third film in the universe, "War" was released in 2019 and starred Hrithik Roshan and Tiger Shroff in pivotal roles. "Pathaan" was the fourth instalment in the Spy Universe franchise which was released in 2023 starring Shah Rukh Khan, Deepika Padukone and John Abraham. "Tiger 3", the fifth instalment in the YRF Spy Universe and the third film in the Tiger series, starring Salman Khan, Katrina Kaif and Emraan Hashmi, released in 2023. "War 2", the sixth film in the YRF Spy Universe, starring Hrithik Roshan, NTR and Kiara Advani, directed by Ayan Mukerji, released on 14 August 2025. "Alpha", the seventh film in the franchise and Hindi cinema‚Äôs first female-led YRF Spy Universe film, starring Alia Bhatt and Sharvari, will release on 25 December 2025.

The first film in the universe, "Ek Tha Tiger," starring Salman Khan and Katrina Kaif was released in 2012, followed by its sequel "Tiger Zinda Hai" in 2017. The third film in the universe, "War" was released in 2019 and starred Hrithik Roshan and Tiger Shroff in pivotal roles. "Pathaan" was the fourth instalment in the Spy Universe franchise which was released in 2023 starring Shah Rukh Khan, Deepika Padukone and John Abraham. "Tiger 3", the fifth instalment in the YRF Spy Universe and the third film in the Tiger series, starring Salman Khan, Katrina Kaif and Emraan Hashmi, released in 2023. "War 2", the sixth film in the YRF Spy Universe, starring Hrithik Roshan, NTR and Kiara Advani, directed by Ayan Mukerji, released on 14 August 2025. "Alpha", the seventh film in the franchise and Hindi cinema‚Äôs first female-led YRF Spy Universe film, starring Alia Bhatt and Sharvari, will release on 25 December 2025.

Movie trailers are designed to give minimal plot detail and to create hype and anticipation. Fan made trailer mashups allow the audience to perform their own cinematic spin on current movie footage. This allows the trailer to focus on a specific actor or portion of the film. It could even change the plot or genre of the film entirely .                                      .----SHINE HUNT CHANNEL----

snippet.title: BIGSHOTS (Official Music Video) | Amit Bhadana, Paradox, Wazir Patar, Vaksh Vimal
snippet.description:
The wait is finally over! üö® 
Aa gaye hai BIGSHOTS ‚Äì a power-packed track featuring Amit Bhadana x Paradox x Wazir Patar 

üëâ Subscribe to Amit Bhadana: https://www.youtube.com/@AmitBhadana

AUDIO CREDITS : 
Singer - Amit Bhadana, Paradox, Wazir Patar 
Lyrics - Amit Bhadana, Paradox, Jasraj Godsmade
Music - Wazir Patar
Composer - Paradox, Wazir Patar 
Mix Master - Dense

VIDEO CREDITS : 
Directed By - Vaksh Vimal (The Frame)
Story, Concept & Creative Director - Amit Bhadana 
Dop - Shinda Singh 
Edit By - Vaksh Vimal (The Frame), Happy (The Frame)
Colorist - Bhumanyu Nehra
Chief AD - Nelson Meena
Set Supervisor - Shivam Saluja
VFX By - Happy (The Frame)
Drone - Happy, Parikshit Tushiyad
Matte painting - Sudeep Das

Production Team (Punjab) :- 
Head of Production - Pankaj Kasana
Line Producer - Gagan Dakala (Dakala Film Production)
Production Assistant - Shivam Saluja, Vikram, Chand, Karan, Kittu, Gursahib, Deep, Param 

Production Team (Bulandshehar, UP) :- 
Head of Production - Pankaj Kasana 
Production Manager - Shivam Saluja
Line Producer - Sumit Bhadana, Sube Bhadana, Sudhir Bhadana
Production Assistant - Deep, Nitin

Paradox‚Äôs Makeup - Vipin Baweja
Paradox‚Äôs Hair - Rohit Diwakar, Vipin  Baweja

Lyrics:
Koi keh desi Koi keh Bigshot 
Kal mile mujhe news waale 3 sau
Main ni zyada gallan baatan kariyan 
Mere baare jo bhi likhna hai likhdo
Kehnde ji jawab dedo ikdo 
Naal saade photuan vi khichlo
Main ni zyada gallan baatan kariyan 
Mere baare jo bhi likhna hai likhdo
Mere baare jo bhi likhna hai likhdo x2
Kal mile mujhe news vaale 3 sau
Mere baare jo bhi 

jo bhi Likhna hai likho saade baare 
Dekhe Tairte tinke dubte kinaare 
Atoot se iraade pair rakhe pure root se milaake 
Keval naam ke ho rishte to door se nibhaate 
Ghoor ke ni jaate milte araam se hain
Sanskaar apne namaste salaam ke hain
Abhi bhi naam se hain 
Abhi bhi kaam ke hain 
Abhi bhi gaam se hain 
Abhi bhi Ram ke hain 
Ameeri hai soch tabhi gareebi jaante hain
Kaafi mile bhi ni log jo kareebi maante hain 
Kamaayi kari bohot jo unhi me baant-te 
Raat me neend lete chain ki zindagi Shaan se hai

Humne kaam kare saare yahan pe badhiya hain
Neki kari bohot aur daala dariya me
Koson door rakhi soch jo ghatiya hai 
Kabhi hili bhi nahi apni buniyaadein 

Abhi baaki Picture dost 
Maine kabhi maare hi nahi trickshots 
Main ni zyada gallan baatan kariyan 
Mere baare jo bhi likhna hai

SADE AUNA JANA PIND REHNDA 
LAGEYA EHNA DA
TATE CHALDE AA BHAU 
MUDHA CHOKDE JINNA DA

RAKHA MATHI MATHI CHAAL
INDUSTRY TO WAKH
FRONT GEEJE (POCKET) VICH KRE NIGRAANI 
TERR'AN (13) LAKH

BAPU JEEP DA SHOKEEN
GEDA FERNI TE MAARE
SHED CH AA TANK LGGA 
JATT NU WANGAARE

RIDE SHER AAWE MERI 
TE ITAR FOOK LAIN
TEDDI PAGG VEKH
JULFAA SAWARDI SHODAIN

KADI LAGPYI SUNAKHI 
MAINU RAFAL PATHANI 
OHNU DEKH DEKH KRE MERA 
MUFFAL SHETANI

RAKHA BEBE JI DA KEHA 
FARMAAN PHULLA TE
SUCCESS HOEYA DISE 
RAAJ NAAM BHULLAN TE

DAR HAINI KOI
MAINU WAR MAUJ DA
SADE TAPE LAUNA
MOTR'AN TE KAM ROJ DA

MAJHE AALEYA TO LOK
KRI JANDI SAADE AA
TAHIO DOUBLE MAGA CH 
ROUND CHADDE AA

OHDI REHMAT AA WADDI 
KHABE HATH CHALE TIME
RIGHT HAND CH ALARM 
KRE BOL BALA KAIM

KYIYA DILLA VICH RAHIYE
BAN HAUL WAJJDE
JITHE RAUNKI SUBAH NE
MAHAUL SAJJDE

BHADANA BHAI
AAJA FIR

Kaam Bade Bade Kar Deve Hai
Geyl Bhole Baba Ke Rehve Hai
Beri Saare Talve Ke Taley Ab
Par Hum Maa Ke Paon Mein Hi Rehve Hai.

Kaam Bade Bade Kar Deve Hai
Geyl Bhole Baba Ke Rehve Hai
Beri Saare Talve Ke Taley Ab
Par Hum Maa Ke Paon Mein Hi Rehve Hai.

#amitbhadana

"Najariya Najar Se" is the latest romantic Bhojpuri song of 2025, released under Times Music Bhojpuri from the upcoming movie "Godfather." Sung by the dynamic duo Khesari Lal Yadav and Priyanka Singh, this love track beautifully captures the essence of romance through heartfelt lyrics and soulful melodies. With its catchy composition and visually stunning official video, the song is quickly becoming a fan favorite across social media and music platforms.

The music video showcases a compelling love story blending traditional Bhojpuri vibes with a modern cinematic touch. Whether you're a fan of Bhojpuri cinema, love songs, or the chart-topping voice of Khesari Lal Yadav, "Najariya Najar Se" is a must-watch and a must-listen.
